{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "biz-purchasing-conversation-office-x5ba",
    "category": "pro",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X5baFS11tU0",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's start, Daddy. What could we make?",
      "zh": "開始吧，爸爸。我們可以做什麼？",
      "ja": "始めましょう、パパ。何を作れるかな？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh. I could just get a pizza. Yes, I think I will.",
      "zh": "哦。我可以直接買個披薩。是的，我想我會這麼做。",
      "ja": "ああ。ピザを買えばいいかな。うん、そうしようと思う。",
      "time": "00:00:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello. Don't cross the owner.",
      "zh": "你好。別惹老闆。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。オーナーを怒らせないで。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One pepperoni pizza on his way.",
      "zh": "一個意大利辣香腸披薩正在準備中。",
      "ja": "ペパロニピザ一枚、ただいま準備中。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on, come on.",
      "zh": "快點，快點。",
      "ja": "さあ、さあ。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go. Keep returning.",
      "zh": "我們走吧。繼續回來。",
      "ja": "行こう。戻り続けて。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm still hungry.",
      "zh": "我還是餓。",
      "ja": "まだお腹が空いてる。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I wonder if I could make my own pizza.",
      "zh": "我想知道我能不能自己做披薩。",
      "ja": "自分でピザを作れるかな。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Pizza, baby.",
      "zh": "披薩，寶貝。",
      "ja": "ピザだよ、ベイビー。",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, bye.",
      "zh": "謝謝，再見。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、さようなら。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why are no orders? This is crazy.",
      "zh": "為什麼沒有訂單？這太瘋狂了。",
      "ja": "なぜ注文がないんだ？これはおかしい。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm losing a fortune.",
      "zh": "我正在損失一大筆錢。",
      "ja": "大損してるよ。",
      "time": "00:06:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you know who I am?",
      "zh": "你知道我是誰嗎？",
      "ja": "私が誰だかわかるか？",
      "time": "00:08:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am Don Castione. The pizza mat.",
      "zh": "我是唐·卡斯蒂奧尼。披薩大師。",
      "ja": "私はドン・カスティオーネ。ピザの達人だ。",
      "time": "00:08:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm putting you out of business. Permanently.",
      "zh": "我要讓你倒閉。永遠的。",
      "ja": "お前の商売を潰してやる。永久に。",
      "time": "00:08:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, that's a good pizza.",
      "zh": "哦，那是個好披薩。",
      "ja": "ああ、それはいいピザだ。",
      "time": "00:09:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You must tell me your secret.",
      "zh": "你一定要告訴我你的秘密。",
      "ja": "秘密を教えてくれ。",
      "time": "00:09:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I put to make you an offer you can't refuse.",
      "zh": "我給你一個你無法拒絕的提議。",
      "ja": "断れない申し出をしよう。",
      "time": "00:09:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is for your machine.",
      "zh": "這是給你的機器。",
      "ja": "これはお前の機械のためだ。",
      "time": "00:09:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No invitation, no entry.",
      "zh": "沒有邀請函，不得入內。",
      "ja": "招待状なしでは入れません。",
      "time": "00:13:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm going in.",
      "zh": "我要進去了。",
      "ja": "入るよ。",
      "time": "00:13:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Invitation, please.",
      "zh": "請出示邀請函。",
      "ja": "招待状をお願いします。",
      "time": "00:14:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good luck.",
      "zh": "祝你好運。",
      "ja": "頑張って。",
      "time": "00:14:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love you.",
      "zh": "我愛你。",
      "ja": "愛してる。",
      "time": "00:15:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Happy birthday, Bean.",
      "zh": "生日快樂，Bean。",
      "ja": "誕生日おめでとう、ビーン。",
      "time": "00:19:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, would sir like to try this new fragrance?",
      "zh": "哦，先生想試試這款新香水嗎？",
      "ja": "ああ、こちらの新しい香水をお試しになりますか？",
      "time": "00:20:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How did they fit, sir?",
      "zh": "先生，穿起來如何？",
      "ja": "お客様、サイズはいかがでしたか？",
      "time": "00:22:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Closing time, sir.",
      "zh": "先生，打烊時間到了。",
      "ja": "閉店時間です、お客様。",
      "time": "00:23:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've been locked in.",
      "zh": "我被鎖在裡面了。",
      "ja": "閉じ込められた。",
      "time": "00:24:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:39:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This has been an expensive week.",
      "zh": "這一週花費不少。",
      "ja": "今週は出費がかさんだ。",
      "time": "00:39:58"
    }
  ]
}